So in this section
we will not go very deep in sorting
the array but we will see how to use the library
functions of sorting using STL

1. method

sort(arr,arr+n);

2 To sort in decreasing order
sort(arr,arr+n, greater<int>() )

Now if you want to sort intervals or some custom use some function

bool compareInterval(interval i1, interval i2){
return (i1.start<i2.start)
}
sort(arr,arr+n,compareInterval)
